{"tid":149920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【13歲少年墮斃】死者讀基道中學 功課較多？副校：一切尚未開始","createTime":"2017-03-09T15:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T05:22:09.000Z","uid":89729,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb07d761df5122c8a2ce3ba86ae4a65f28caa6aa","tid":149920,"uid":89729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T15:29:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2015/9/23</span><br />\n土瓜灣今早有13歲朱姓少年墮樓身亡。中華基督教會基道中學發出新聞稿，確認今早有朱姓學生墮樓離世，並已由危機處理小組老師透過校內廣播將事件通知全體學生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者剛升讀中一，事發前和家人曾就學業問題爭執。基道中學呂副校長被問到功課是否較多，他表示「一切尚未開始」，又指公布消息後未收到學生個別求助，會密切留意死者同班同學。<br />\n<br />\n基道中學署理校長在新聞稿中表示，今早從有關家長口中得知事件，全校師生極為難過，老師、學生輔導主任、社工等人已為同學提供輔導。校方已發出家長信，提醒家長未來一周留意學生情緒。<br />\n<br />\n校方又指，目前不宜作任何揣測。<br />\n<br />\n掌握最新消息，請Like「明報即時新聞」fb專頁！ http:// <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=7696b421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/</a> mingpaoinews<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E3%80%9013%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E5%A2%AE%E6%96%83%E3%80%91%E6%AD%BB%E8%80%85%E8%AE%80%E5%9F%BA%E9%81%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E3%80%80%E5%8A%9F%E8%AA%B2%E8%BC%83%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%9F%E5%89%AF%E6%A0%A1%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%AA%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B/web_tc/article/20150923/s00001/1442999307145#sthash.1a5nSbxf.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E3%2580%259013%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%2596%2583%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25AE%2580%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2581%2593%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E8%25BC%2583%25E5%25A4%259A%25EF%25BC%259F%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%25A0%25A1%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2588%2587%25E5%25B0%259A%25E6%259C%25AA%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A7%258B%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20150923%2Fs0000